text: Heavy flooding in the Central Coast and Sydney areas of New South Wales, Australia, began in early July 2022. Around 85,000 people were quickly forced out of their homes by the flooding. ==References== Category:July 2022 events Category:2022 floods Category:2022 in Australia Category:2020s in New South Wales Category:2022 disasters in Oceania Category:Floods in Australia
title: 2022 New South Wales floods
